column9:
The receptionist girl was very friendly and helpful;
Reasonable price;
They have vending machine that sells water and drinks cheaper than in convenient stores, which is rare to see as hostels always overcharge extra services;
Interesting neighborhood.

Location is very accessible to MRT; 
Along with cheap set of foods (more of Indian foods)
With nearby ATM, grocery store (good value), market

column8:
1) There was no window in the room, that was not obvious at the room picture;
2) One time a towel smelled badly;
3) Very noisy. No noice insulation at all, couldn’t sleep at night.
